caption.body: “Time, Turn, and Light” by #WoodyDeOthello depicts ambiguous sets of hands interacting with everyday objects such as clocks, a flashlight, a candle, and a doorknob. These objects are rendered in an uncanny fashion with a sense of play, emotional intuition, and surrealism that provokes viewers to reimagine themselves and the way they view the world around them.  “Time, Turn, and Light” by #WoodyDeOthello online at: https://bit.ly/3kiuVFq
